data.description: Immaculately Clean with this Perfect Cassidy Floor Plan by Crescent Homes. Large and Open with a Beautiful Screened in Porch, Master Bedroom on First Floor, and Large Flex Area Upstairs. Updates and Upgrades include; New Tankless Hotwater Heater, Fiber Optic Internet, New LVP Floors in Master Bedroom, and More. Granite Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, Tons of Countertop Space and Grade A Quality Cabinets. This Home also has a Large Attic Space Upstairs Offering Plenty of Storage Space. This is a Must See!
